data.description: This lovely Kite floor plan offers 3 bedrooms & 2.5 baths. Kitchen features gorgeous cabinets, beautiful granite countertops, stainless steel appliances & island. Owners suite showcases a tray ceiling, fan, walk-in closet, cultured marble vanity & 5 ft shower. Add'l features include gas log fireplace & large playroom! Entertaining patio overlooks the spacious backyard. Amenities include pools, gyms & golf with your FSC Membership!
